## Third-party component libraries

`hw-trv/kicad-libs/` contains reference files (not the original
library packages) pointing to third-party CAD symbol/footprint/3D
model exports (from SamacSys, Ultra Librarian, and SnapEDA) used
while designing this project. Those vendor files are NOT included
in this repository and are NOT covered by this license -- they
remain under their respective vendors' own terms, which generally
permit using the parts in your own design but restrict redistributing
the bare library files themselves. See the `.kicad-lib-source.txt`
file for each part for sourcing details.

